T02TD3661E:265a-1: m'a r'i tsyee de b'i s'a dha nam /
T02TD3661E:265a-3: lha mo 'od zer can gyi sgrub thabs /
T02TD3661E:265b-0: @265b lha mo 'od zer can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3661E:265b-1: de la dang por nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bsams la /
T02TD3661E:265b-2: de'i steng du sa bon lnga pa'i lnga pa la /
T02TD3661E:265b-3: dang po'i gnyis pa rdzogs par byas la /
T02TD3661E:265b-4: zla ba phyed pa dang thig les brgyan par bsam /
T02TD3661E:265b-5: de las byung ba'i lha mo 'od zer can sku mdog dmar ba /
T02TD3661E:265b-12: steng gi dbu phag gdong nag po /
T02TD3661E:265b-17: dbu skra dmar ser gyen du brdzes pa /
T02TD3661E:265b-18: sbrul gyi zhags pa dang stag lpags kyi sham thabs can /
T02TD3661E:265b-19: bgegs rnams ltung bar mdzad pa /
T02TD3661E:265b-20: kha dog sna tshogs pa'i shing rta la g-yon brkyang bas bzhugs pa /
T02TD3661E:265b-21: phyag g-yas pa na ral gri dang /
T02TD3661E:265b-24: mda' dang rdo rje rtse gcig pa dang /
T02TD3661E:265b-26: g-yon pa sdigs mdzub zhags pa dang bcas pa dang /
T02TD3661E:265b-27: thod pa dang aa shva ka'i yal ga dang /
T02TD3661E:265b-32: mdun du shing zlum po'i dbus su lag pa gnyis sdigs mdzub bsgreng bar bsams la /
T02TD3661E:265b-33: bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das ma yum 'od zer can yin no zhes pa'i nga rgyal bskyed par bya'o //
T02TD3661E:265b-34: de nas phyag rgya bcing bar bya ste /
T02TD3661E:265b-35: rdo rje thal mo kha sbyar la /
T02TD3661E:265b-36: gung mo gnyis gshibs la myu gur byas te /
T02TD3661E:265b-37: mthe bong gnyis skyil mo krung du bsnol mdzub mo gnyis rtse mor dgug par bya'o //
T02TD3661E:265b-38: de nas bzlas pa'i sngags ni /
T02TD3661E:265b-39: aom m'a r'i tsyee m'am h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD3661E:265b-40: lha mo 'od zer can gyi sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
